This project is a local-first Obsidian-style project memory and handoff starter kit for AI coding agents.

Core public concepts documented by this repository include:

- local-first AI agent memory vault
- project master, handoff, decision ledger, and error ledger structure
- project-prefixed Obsidian graph hygiene
- reusable agent adapter prompts
- OpenHands rebirth policy as a memory and recovery contract

